reviewText:
I have the VCR version for a long time, but the tape broke.  I tried to fix it, but I can only watch from the break forward-not from the beginning.
Thank you for the CD version.  It should last a longer time.
I like this DVD.  Not alot of chit chat like some of them and there is concern that you are lifting with the proper form so as to avoid injury.  I recommend it for those starting out or at any level.
